{"tid":1313442,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[廣傳] 勇武前先睇吓呢幾條片","createTime":"2019-07-13T18:33:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T19:34:50.000Z","uid":157063,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"2c68e5350e931fa923458abc8d1f188916919f87","tid":1313442,"uid":157063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T18:33:38.000Z","msg":"香港人開始想衝破勇武呢條心理關口<br />\n但係以下幾段片<br />\n比大家認識吓香港狗察既訓練內容<br />\n2006年 已經有防暴教學<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zKVbqz7i54A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DzKVbqz7i54A&d=mHuePEBkC2D1nBcDBUtULxZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=2fcf9246\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zKVbqz7i54A</a><br />\n到今時今日示威都仲未出現既野 (刀、汽油彈)<br />\n佢地已經演習緊<br />\n<br />\n長盾<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IJwlHM0NwTc&amp;t=7s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DIJwlHM0NwTc%26t%3D7s&d=mHuePEBkC2D1nBcDBUtULxZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=06d07027\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IJwlHM0NwTc&amp;t=7s</a><br />\n圓盾<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hlwuml2K7Kk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dhlwuml2K7Kk&d=mHuePEBkC2D1nBcDBUtULxZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=e4a02398\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hlwuml2K7Kk</a><br />\n<br />\n破解既方法交比大家研究吓<br />\n不過大家都知啲狗會mon post<br />\n所以請自行從其他途徑研究<br />\n<br />\n最後陣型<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kLvnyj_vSa8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DkLvnyj_vSa8&d=mHuePEBkC2D1nBcDBUtULxZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=d19815e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kLvnyj_vSa8</a><br />\n<br />\n純粹想拋磚引玉<br />\n等大家分享多啲唔同國家既防暴教學<br />\n知己知彼"},{"pid":"7c7373ef18add0639e1f02a3ee6ecdf49f9a2d8d","tid":1313442,"uid":157063,"li