 />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家要記住，一日未完全令政府承諾呢七大訴求，一日呢場運動都唔可以完"},{"pid":"1faa07ecd7db17d8c778449c3ade9d7d13b67c09","tid":1313442,"uid":138978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T19:34:50.000Z","msg":"push"}]}